      "description": "Offered is a concours-level E92 M3, featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 with an 8,400 RPM redline. This example is mechanically flawless, with documented preventative rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service to ensure longitudinal integrity. The factory paint retains its deep luster with no evidence of thermal cycling fatigue on the carbon fiber roof. Power is managed by a recalibrated M-DCT dual-clutch transmission and a variable M-differential lock, providing exceptional torque vectoring. The suspension remains factory-spec with Electronic Damping Control (EDC) maintaining original valve responsiveness. A truly unmolested, turnkey masterpiece for the serious collector.",
